snippet.title: The Adventures of Sam Carlisle: The Hunt for the Lost Treasure Gameplay Trailer #1
snippet.description:
The Official Teaser trailer for THE ADVENTURES OF SAM CARLISLE: THE HUNT FOR THE LOST TREASURE. The game will be available 6 October 2017. for more information.
